    <stitle>HYDRO-MAX II BRAKE MONITOR SYSTEM - DESCRIPTION - PUMP AND MOTOR ASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>PUMP AND MOTOR ASSEMBLY</title>
        <para>The pump and motor assembly provides hydraulic pressure for the brake booster assembly when the engine is
            not running and the key switch is on; when the engine is not running, the key switch is off, and the brake
            pedal is depressed; or the engine is running and the power steering pump or system has failed.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
